    <div class="module">
        It's tough to switch gears and think ahead to summer, but if you want your teen to attend a summer learning program or get a job, now's the time to act.
        <br/>
        <ul class="noHover">

            <li>
                Want a program that's out of the ordinary? We've tracked down some <gsweb:articlelink articleId="313">exotic summer alternatives</gsweb:articlelink>.
            </li>
            <li>
                If you're considering teen travel programs, here's <gsweb:articlelink articleId="545">what to look for</gsweb:articlelink>.
            </li>
            <li>
                Stumped for job ideas? Here are <gsweb:articlelink articleId="536">some to get your teen started</gsweb:articlelink>.
