    <div class="module">
        If your child is a senior waiting to hear from college admissions offices, it may
        be knuckle-biting time at your house. Here's some advice to get through the process:
        <ul class="noHover">
            <li>
                Don't race your child to the mailbox.
            </li>
            <li>
                Don't open college mail addressed to your child.
            </li>
            <li>
                Understand that your child has options even if no college accepts her.
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div align="right">
